## Identity Linking — Merge Multiple OAuth Providers

Users can link multiple login methods to one account.

```typescript
// User already logged in with Google, wants to also link GitHub
const { error } = await supabase.auth.linkIdentity({ provider: 'github' })
// Redirects to GitHub OAuth, then links to existing account

// List all linked identities for current user
const { data: { user } } = await supabase.auth.getUser()
const identities = user?.identities  // Array of linked providers
// [{ provider: 'google', ... }, { provider: 'github', ... }]

// Unlink an identity
await supabase.auth.unlinkIdentity(identityToRemove)
```

