## Rate Limits (Auth Endpoints)

Supabase applies rate limits per project per hour. If exceeded, users get 429 errors.

| Endpoint | Free tier | Paid tier |
|---|---|---|
| Sign up | 30/hour | 360/hour |
| Sign in | 30/hour | 360/hour |
| Magic link | 30/hour | 360/hour |
| Password reset | 30/hour | 360/hour |
| OTP | 30/hour | 360/hour |

**If users hit rate limits**: Upgrade Supabase plan, or add CAPTCHA.

```typescript
// Add CAPTCHA (hCaptcha or Turnstile) to reduce spam
const { data, error } = await supabase.auth.signUp({
  email,
  password,
  options: { captchaToken },  // from hCaptcha or Cloudflare Turnstile widget
})
```
